description: Single Family! Sun filled, stylish and versatile, this updated 3-bed, 2.5-bath West Side home in South Boston blends character with modern comfort. The spacious living room with fireplace and custom built-ins flows to the kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, custom cabinetry and sunroom—ideal for dining, a home office, or cozy retreat. Step outside to a private, renovated backyard designed for easy entertaining. First floor updated powder room. Upstairs, two large bedrooms include one with a fireplace and one with a deck, plus a full bath and full sized washer/dryer. The top floor is a private primary suite with en-suite bath, walk-in closet, and sitting area. This home offers hardwood floors, air conditioning, custom closets, full basement, and plenty of storage. Flexible layout offers potential for a 4th bedroom and roof deck.  All just moments from shops, dining, gyms, area attractions, public transportation and more!
